name: タヨ・ポーラ 🌸 (Taylor's Version) (From The Vault)
text:
[@joyarmadamba](https://twitter.com/joyarmadamba/) [@roytang](https://twitter.com/roytang/) Not sure if it's possible, kasi it's more of account users than addresses that are the main identifiers for these services.



Pero the idea is for these services have a "disable COD" option. Would be great if kaya i-flag by address rather than user.
